{"tid":92184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯","createTime":"2017-01-23T11:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T13:26:32.000Z","uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17c194a9e7badfa9140047777699ebf0131213bb","tid":92184,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"2017年01月23日10:15&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n美國阿拉巴馬州眾議員羅傑斯（Mike Rogers）本月初在眾議院提出法案，建議美國退出聯合國，不過他在2015年早提過類似提案，但未獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯本月3日和6名議員聯名在眾院提出《2017恢復美國主權法案》，內容提及要求美國退出聯合國、不再容許聯合國把總部設在美國紐約，附加條款也包括退出世界衛生組織。<br />\n<br />\n如法案在國會兩院過關，走完流程，美國兩年後就要退出聯合國。不過這項法案並非第一次提出，過去羅傑斯的類似構想並未獲得大多數同僚支持，胎死腹中。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170123/1041454/聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170123%2F1041454%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%8A%EF%BC%9F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E9%80%80%E8%81%AF&d=JxDRBE6j8SgAGaAZIKTA0QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=80dfc42d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170123/1041454/聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170123/640_b56a374fdd3e42c4456d5f42734a396b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170123%2F640_b56a374fdd3e42c4456d5f42734a396b.jpg&h=d64acdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9125f1ef5e9f03594acb186ed06176d4adfc60b8","tid":92184,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"中國組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea647c88933dc0ee67dd6195de3e5abdaeeb528","tid":92184,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"孤立主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ffff49763ebfd406a9d3169028d13e8bccc40d","tid":92184,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:00:52.000Z","msg":"Splendid isolation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b092346f2e89b3b66714a79954f5246bde02cd","tid":92184,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"其實美國推出聯合國，另外成立個文明世界國家聯盟是件好事"},{"pid":"8b2916733a5ad5047c153b1863eee2624761877e","tid":92184,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實美國推出聯合國，另外成立個文明世界國家聯盟是件好事</blockquote><br />\n咪弱智啦"},{"pid":"f51dc2b0450cca84b310b817957618981d9ecdf0","tid":92184,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"咁撚好笑<br />\n佢老美真係以為自己係美國隊長<br />\n唔簽英雄法案啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}